libbtc
------------------------------------------
Libbtc is a very portable C library for creating and manipulating bitcoin data
structures and interacting with the p2p network.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.11.2-1
  libbtc-devel-0.1+git20181004-1bl1
  libbtc0-0.1+git20181004-1bl1
  libevent2.0_5-2.0.22-1
  liblogdb0-0.1+git20160906-1bl2
  libsecp256k1_0-0.1+git20180601-1bl1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-10-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.31.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-6
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/libbtc/libbtc

Canonical download:
  git://github.com/libbtc/libbtc.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libbtc-0.1+git20181004-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libbtc-0.1+git20181004-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libbtc-0.1+git20181004-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbtc-0.1+git20181004-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbtc0-0.1+git20181004-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbtc-devel-0.1+git20181004-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libbtc)
  /usr/bin/bitcoin-send-tx.exe
  /usr/bin/bitcoin-spv.exe
  /usr/bin/bitcointool.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libbtc.README
  /usr/share/doc/libbtc/README.md

(libbtc0)
  /usr/bin/cygbtc-0.dll

(libbtc-devel)
  /usr/include/btc/aes256_cbc.h
  /usr/include/btc/base58.h
  /usr/include/btc/bip32.h
  /usr/include/btc/block.h
  /usr/include/btc/btc.h
  /usr/include/btc/buffer.h
  /usr/include/btc/chainparams.h
  /usr/include/btc/ctaes.h
  /usr/include/btc/ecc.h
  /usr/include/btc/ecc_key.h
  /usr/include/btc/hash.h
  /usr/include/btc/headersdb.h
  /usr/include/btc/headersdb_file.h
  /usr/include/btc/net.h
  /usr/include/btc/netspv.h
  /usr/include/btc/portable_endian.h
  /usr/include/btc/protocol.h
  /usr/include/btc/random.h
  /usr/include/btc/ripemd160.h
  /usr/include/btc/script.h
  /usr/include/btc/segwit_addr.h
  /usr/include/btc/serialize.h
  /usr/include/btc/tool.h
  /usr/include/btc/tx.h
  /usr/include/btc/utils.h
  /usr/include/btc/vector.h
  /usr/include/btc/wallet.h
  /usr/lib/libbtc.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libbtc.pc

